  "Description": {
    "English": "A solemn power radiates from this ancient carving. Though the imagery is simple and the rendering rough, the meaning of the glyph has mathematical precision.<br><br>This is glyph <span class=\"name name-special\">1</span> of <span class=\"name name-special\">16</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "这古老的雕刻散发着庄严的力量，尽管图像简单，形式朴素，但符文的含义却有着数学的精度。<br><br>这是<span class=\"name name-special\">16</span>枚符文中的<span class=\"name name-special\">1</span>号符文。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "古老雕刻散發出莊嚴的力量。雖然意象簡單、手法粗糙，表達出的符號含意卻如數學般精準。<br><br>這是 <span class=\"name name-special\">16</span> 個符號中的第 <span class=\"name name-special\">1</span> 個。"
  },
